courses.description:
The internet offers countless opportunities, but it also presents challenges when it comes to protecting your finances, personal information, and identity from scams. With the right knowledge, you can confidently navigate the web, recognizing and avoiding potential threats with ease.
This course is designed to arm you with the knowledge and skills needed to identify and combat scams across a variety of modern digital platforms. Each module is packed with quizzes and downloadable resources to ensure you learn, retain, and can quickly refresh your knowledge whenever necessary.


Course Modules Include:
Scams in Emails: Master the skill of identifying phishing scams, fake online meetings, and business impersonators. With our investigative tactics and quizzes, you'll learn not to be puzzled by suspicious emails;
Scams in Messages & Calls: Gain insights into tax refund scams, investment calls, and fake parcel delivery messages. Learn to distinguish between genuine and scammy calls, even those using advanced AI-generated voices;
Scams in Social Media: Navigate the social media landscape confidently as you learn to identify job scams, social media lotteries, investment scams, and account thefts. Our quizzes will test your knowledge and keep you sharp;
Scams in Digital Banking: Since banks typically do not compensate for losses due to customer faults, this module will equip you to avoid expensive mistakes. Learn about AI-generated scams, fake banking calls, and more;
Scams in Traveling Apps: Uncover the truth behind fake rentals, scammy accommodation listings, and airlines without licenses. Discover scammers' tactics and the hidden costs of supposed "free" vacations;
Scams in Online Shopping: Identify fake retailers, fraudulent discounts, and payment issue scams. Learn the underlying logic of pre-order and delivery scams to shop online safely;
Scams in Dating Apps: Go beyond the basics to understand emotional traps, stalking, and other common tactics scammers use on dating apps. Learn to spot fake profiles with expert precision.


By the end of this course, you'll have a well-rounded understanding of various scams, how they operate, and, most importantly, how to protect yourself and your loved ones in this online world. Enroll today and become a pro at unmasking scams!

